</p></tsCauses><tsDiagnose id="GUID-717CE06C-80EB-4724-8B69-C0F8464CD2D8" class="- topic/section tsTroubleshooting/tsDiagnose "><p class="- topic/p ">Check the electrical connections of the sensor. 
